Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.53,0:01:36.86,Top,,0,0,0,,At long last, the long-awaited swimming pool \Nhas been completed.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.90,0:01:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To mark the occasion there will be \Na medley relay between the forms.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.85,0:01:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The anchor for each team \Nwill be that form’s mistress.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.66,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means our anchor in the first form \Nwill be Miss Roberts?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... exactly what it means.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.65,0:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, swimming lessons \Nwill form part of P.T.,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.06,0:02:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but before that, the pupils are to give their views \Non what sort of swimsuits they would like.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.60,0:02:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The middle one, of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.12,0:02:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the one on the left!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.89,0:02:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly the one on the right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.81,0:02:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This takes me back...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.56,0:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fond of swimming \Nwhen I was a girl, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Mam'zelle?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, frankly... only a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.01,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Blimey! Mam’zelle was never any good \Nat sports of any kind.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.73,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are strong swimmers!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.23,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We might even win!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.30,0:03:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? {sounds kinda weird but idk what else to put here, "what makes you think so" is too long}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.95,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Miss Roberts \Nis said to be a marvellous swimmer.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at that!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.28,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.88,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, which of us was faster?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.72,0:03:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,About the same, I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was faster!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, I was!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Janet!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.80,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Janet wins, because she kept her stroke to the very end. {??? dunno what she means, probably something about swimming that i don't understand: until the end, properly did stroking share, janet's win}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye now. {? dewa?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crumbs.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can one believe a word \Nof what Mam’zelle says at this rate? {?? idk, probably implies "she's so bad at sports, she wouldn't know who won"}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It was me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real, I'm sure I was faster!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, it was me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Alison?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren’t you getting up on the starting block?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t swim!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alison!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.30,0:04:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you told us yesterday you could.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that because it was \Ntoo much bother to explain. {assuming that}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.65,0:04:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.90,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you told us you went \Nto the seaside all last summer!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I do fancy the sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.14,0:04:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Going out in yachts, walking along the sands, \Ncollecting pretty shells...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.37,0:04:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never went in the water?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.87,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother says I ought to learn to swim properly like Pat and Isabel, but I simply don’t like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you must have special coaching.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Special coaching?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.30,0:05:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we have a splendid pool, \Nevery St. Clare’s pupil must learn to swim.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.67,0:05:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the rule of the school.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.07,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But one can still marry, \Neven if she can’t swim... {meaning "the purpose of this school is to bring up proper brides"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.16,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Nothing. \NJust thinking out loud. {??? lit: this is my story/talk}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam’zelle!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.36,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alison!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You mustn’t help her yet! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.04,0:05:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But she’s going under! {? probably drowning}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch what happens!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t just stand and look!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.24,0:05:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I said no and no it must be!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.22,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s swimming!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alison!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.67,0:06:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?\NI thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.86,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But you swam, didn’t you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s what matters.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.85,0:06:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate Mam’zelle!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alison!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miss. Fifty-five B.C.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar crossed the Rhine and invaded Britain... {?? lmao, idk if it's meant to the joke or they unironically mistook britania for germania}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.28,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you to read?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.84,0:06:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not it at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.02,0:06:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Mam’zelle pushed you into the pool.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.23,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed. \NI very nearly drowned.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.43,0:07:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least you can swim now, can’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.50,0:07:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s often said the best way to teach a non-swimmer is to throw her straight into the water.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.25,0:07:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! I can only swim now \Nbecause I had the talent in me all along! {/predisposition}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.88,0:07:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, girls, the prize for the victory \Nin the upcoming commemorative tournament
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.62,0:07:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,has been fixed to be \Na magnificent cup this big!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you’ve already won because of Miss Roberts, but don't be too smug.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.66,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the fifth form \Nhave me as their form mistress!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're taking part too, Miss Lewis?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And how good of a swimmer are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s what I do best.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the crawl.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.55,0:08:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the fifth form \Ncan count on their several
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.32,0:08:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,formidable all-round athletes, such as Belinda or Pamela.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.32,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So we’re up against truly formidable rivals.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.04,0:08:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Which form will claim the coveted cup \Nof the very first commemorative tournament?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of us must strive for victory!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And we’ll not be beaten!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on we’ll practise every afternoon. {/after school too}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed! {sansei}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.08,0:08:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the fifth form!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But we won't be beaten!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Mam'zelle?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That shouting distracted me. {/cheering}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.40,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I had hoped to find somewhere quiet to read.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the woods yonder would suit you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go there.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.08,0:09:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny—those cheers give me a thrill.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren’t you going into the woods, Mam'zelle?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.78,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness me, this isn’t the wood at all, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish of me to wander here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Pat! Relax your shoulders!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.47,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this, move lightly...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.39,0:09:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh. I'm watching the birds.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Vraiment? I never thought you’d have such a hobby.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.65,0:10:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rare bird that is seldom seen in these parts.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see too!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It’s flown!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.93,0:10:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t lose sight of it—keep after it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where is it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The pool!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The pool?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.21,0:10:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Swimming.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.01,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Swimming? That bird?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The first form team will be as follows:
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,First, Hilary—crawl.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Joan—butterfly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Kathleen—backstroke.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Doris—breaststroke.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Janet—crawl.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.39,0:10:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Isabel—breaststroke.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.21,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly, Pat—crawl.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven in all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right—we’ll do our best!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty metres each, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.43,0:11:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes—save for me, the anchor, \Nwho swims a hundred.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? A hundred meters, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.91,0:11:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.07,0:11:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve chosen by watching you swim, \Nbut those not picked mustn’t feel downhearted.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.18,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Downhearted? I’m relieved!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.67,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Those not on the team—\Ncheer us on, won’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.61,0:11:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts, we’ve yet to see you swim!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So you haven’t.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well—let’s to the pool.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.11,0:11:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s Miss Lewis!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, Miss Roberts!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're going toe-to-toe! {/equal}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Roberts! {? dunno what english word to choose}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.69,0:12:07.38,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Roberts!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Roberts!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a decent battle, first form. {? iishobu ne?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the victory is ours!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,Like we'll ever lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow decides it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The second form are already all fired up,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.43,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,after vowing the first commemorative tournament cup shall be theirs.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but the sixth form are fired up too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.30,0:12:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, they want to claim the cup \Nas a farewell prize before graduating.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Every form is bound to be after it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.87,0:12:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But looking at the line-up from first to sixth,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems the real battle \Nwill be between us and the fifth form.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But our anchor might just be \Nwhat gives us that critical edge.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.37,0:13:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite so! Miss Roberts is faster \Nthan Miss Lewis, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.02,0:13:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miss Lewis declared \Nshe would not be beaten in the real race.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.11,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, it’s certain to be a fine contest.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.00,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky for us, Mam’zelle isn’t our anchor. {/homeroom teacher}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were, we’d totally be nailed to last place.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Too true!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, tomorrow \Nwe’ll do our utmost for victory!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.88,0:13:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.92,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, fifth form!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.94,0:14:02.86,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Go, go, fifth form!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.05,0:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, first form!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.42,0:14:14.59,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Go, go, first form!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.59,0:14:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{i refuse}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is each form gathered in full strength?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to march in, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Thomas?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the anchor mistresses?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They shall enter from the other side.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Parade of competitors!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.33,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{fuck this}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.55,0:15:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight! Don't let us down! \NFor victory! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.95,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the anchors!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{ganbare}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mam'zelle?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts had to leave for the Ministry of Education on official school business.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.86,0:15:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Her meeting ran long, \Nand she could not return in time for the race.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.28,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam’zelle has kindly agreed to stand in.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.07,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s outrageous!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A plot, surely!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Now we’re doomed to last place.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What was all our practice for, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.87,0:16:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we must at least show our spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What spirit is there to show? {lit: There's no way to show it}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.18,0:16:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We must at least lead until the final lap! {/before it's anchor's turn}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.12,0:16:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll prove the first form is the one \Nthat's truly the strongest.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.19,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, with or without the cup!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On your marks!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.88,0:17:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Hilary!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.56,0:17:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilary’s in the lead!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Pamela’s overtaken her!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.86,0:17:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax your shoulders, Hilary! Relax them!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's next? Go, Joan! {????? no clue, doitsu da? dochira? could be anything, maybe "we're tied!"}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoulders loose!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.56,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.53,0:17:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Kathleen!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.96,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Doris!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that’s it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.91,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Janet!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.76,0:17:59.26,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Shoulders relaxed. Perfectly relaxed!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.26,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.25,0:18:02.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,Geez, is that the only thing she knows? {lit: because only that}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,The fifth form are closing in!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Janet!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.91,0:18:18.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh, crumbs! She’s overtaken me! \NAll right, we'll be first, even if only for a moment! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.63,0:18:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go Isabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.92,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid, Isabel, keep it up! {????? nc what's first word}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,We must hold the lead at any cost!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat's in the lead!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.92,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! We're first again!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.30,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! We're top ranked!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Until Mam'zelle's run... {lit: mamzelle is...}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.47,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s not surfacing!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She’s sinking!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What shall we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.79,0:19:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Mam'zelle! {don't see a way to avoid this}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.73,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, someone must save her!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.33,0:19:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.65,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam’zelle is swimming beneath the water!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.16,0:19:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Such speed!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.83,0:19:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And such grace! {lit: incredibly fast. and also pretty}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If she finishes like this…
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.37,0:20:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! We’ve done it! {????? sugoi yo?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.01,0:20:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam’zelle! How on earth \Ndo you swim so well?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to tell you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.73,0:20:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam’zelle was once hailed \Nas a prodigy of French swimming.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.59,0:20:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Backstroke was her speciality, \Nand she was even chosen for the Olympic team.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But she turned it down.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.73,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Mam’zelle chose the life\N of a teacher over that of an athlete.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.67,0:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been a hard and painful choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why didn’t you ever tell us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.78,0:20:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam’zelle, for all her appearance, \Nis not one to boast of past glories.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.67,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"For all her appearance"—\Nwhat do you mean by that, Headmistress?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.79,0:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I should like to know that!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.11,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can talk this over some other time.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But one thing I can say for certain: I was happy to swim with you all with all my strength!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you swim with us more from now on?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oui.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam'zelle!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.13,0:21:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep this victory cup in your room.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.12,0:21:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.59,0:21:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was thanks to you that we won.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.51,0:21:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But this belongs to everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.32,0:22:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam’zelle, this is your Olympics—\Nthe Olympics of a teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.12,0:23:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat, that Miss Walker has given us \Nthe most awful assignment!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.12,0:23:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Making a trinket box out of boards— {komonoire = accessory case}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.24,0:23:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and on top of all the other homework!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.16,0:23:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes ages to make even a plain box,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.59,0:23:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and she’s given us only a week!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.56,0:23:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But Vera and Doris \Nhave come up with a clever idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.16,0:23:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What sort of idea?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.17,0:23:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They asked a furniture shop \Nto make the trinket box for them.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.55,0:23:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? But that’s not allowed!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.20,0:23:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twins at St. Clare's:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,“Miss Walker’s Gift.” {ウォーカー先生の贈り物}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.26,0:24:04.26,Note,,0,0,0,,Episode 21 \NMiss Walker’s Gift
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.67,0:24:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t miss it!
